public class UnreifiedRelationImpl extends RelationImpl implements UnreifiedRelation
An implementation of the model object 'Unreified Relation'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Owning Vocabulary
  • Owned Specializations
  • Sources
  • Targets
  • Reverse Relation
  • Functional
  • Inverse Functional
  • Symmetric
  • Asymmetric
  • Reflexive
  • Irreflexive
  • Transitive
